    <title>AI and Games episode 50: Alien: Isolation Revisited</title>
    <link>https://www.patreon.com/posts/ai-and-games-50-37033242</link>
    <description>&lt;p&gt;Hey everyone,&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;Here is the third - and hopefully final pass - at episode 50 as I revisit Alien: Isolation.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;The video went through several edits since the original version went out to Goomba+ patrons last week.  I added some new footage as well as some changes to help better promote Matt Filer&apos;s OpenCAGE mod.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;This is a weird entry in that it kinda relies on you having seen the original, but I do make efforts to recap the first video.  That said, there is a lot of new information in here and I hope that proves interesting.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;Hope you find it interesting!  We&apos;ll be launching it this Wednesday.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;- Tommy&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;</description>
